8. **Use Virtual Credit Cards**: When making purchases online, use virtual credit cards or prepaid cards to avoid linking your real financial information to your online activities.

9. **Stay Informed About Online Security**: Keep up-to-date with the latest security practices and updates from technology companies. This includes software updates and security patches.

10. **Consider Using Tor or a Virtual Private Network (VPN)**: These tools can help anonymize your internet traffic and protect your privacy by routing your connection through multiple servers.

